Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Sewing Machine Cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.42,0:00:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise... I'll never give you my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a silent night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.76,0:00:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eclipse was beginnin'
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The overlapping moments
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We might believe them to be eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's darker than black
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The labyrinthine sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Begs for light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I bite your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The impulse eats away at me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... Can I... Can I... Who am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Libido erases my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Into darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have fallen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a hideous form
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.76,0:01:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If my human tears have dried
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.17,0:01:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NOur crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wets our bond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We share our weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NWe share our weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we two live on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Licking each other's wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Defining each other's life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirsting for love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The main PC is on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouroboros
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We can boot it up and get the member list,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will take five minutes to unlock it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And five more to copy the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So when will we be breaking into\Nthe CCC hideout, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the squad leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When do you think would be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The sooner the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If they catch on to us, they'll erase the list and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Five was Ushio from C Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll ask their leader, Takimoto,\Nto help us keep him busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop Kikuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we can let you join the raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But on the other hand, we are short-staffed,\Nso would you keep lookout for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hope you'll leave the sniper rifle at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Jill are grounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you break the deployment ban again,\Nyou will be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only taking humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be any devils in the CCC.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're up against humans, humans can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been given notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They understand you were in danger\Nthe other day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the event that a devil\Nignores the deployment ban,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,if they transform and engage in violence,\Ncause injury, or drink blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:03:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they will be immediately relieved of their duty,\Nregardless of their reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They will thenceforth be placed\Nunder strict surveillance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and forbidden to make contact with\Nhumans for the foreseeable future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?\NAre they going to quarantine us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing you'll be under 24-hour surveillance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and banned from visiting,\Nor even calling or emailing, anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, everyone... dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Glorious food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we couldn't make anything more elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When a guy actually tells you to investigate him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,he knows you're not gonna find any dirt on him\Nwithout some serious digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ishimaru, Megumi\N{\an5}Lieutenant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Anzai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. I made it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a utility belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, but I guess you won't be deploying,\Nso you don't have to use it if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You had one, but I didn't think\Nit was the best thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for carrying those nail protectors\Nyou got from Mr. Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you could put the protectors here,\Nand it would be easier to get them on quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe it won't be that easy after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Anzai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You have it backwards.\NI should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You just gave me a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}I know it's late,\N{\an5}but Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I mean it when I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really so glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No. This is one time I have to insist-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll need you on the lookout team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishimaru, you can't-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll just be standing watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on to this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. I want you to stay with Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of her for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now commencing our raid on the CCC hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Objective: obtain the member list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ishimaru and Sawazaki,\Nwith Asami as backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking Zero Nine to the main computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Seven is on a building\N100 yards south of the hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai is on a building 500 yards to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagi, you stand by near the hideout, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, would you please take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be as close to him as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a-! Lee! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time. We're going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a strange noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Seven! Can you see the river out back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in my blind spot! I heard a splash, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Those strange noises were gunshots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He used a silencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the same bullets we use in Division 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If that man was from Division 5,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,would he deliberately let us\Nhear his voice like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're not the most uncommon bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, where's the computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-the second room from the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they were homeless,\Nand they were squatting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's too much dirt on his feet for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have come off if he was\Nwalking around in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone killed some homeless people...\Nin the CCC hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Those gunshots...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There were three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the third bullet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no third bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki! Hey! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Jill are grounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you break the deployment ban again,\Nyou will be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But he bit me-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ishimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've encountered five transformed devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two bodies in the hallway,\Nbut the devils aren't even looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The bodies in the hall aren't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one more body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The man killed by the third bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:10:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The five devils ganged up on the human,\Nso they could all drink his blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So just one of them is human?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll make sure not to look at him\Nwhen I come to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your exact position!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bleeding, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I weren't, the second they find out\Nyou deployed, you'll be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stay away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come, Sawazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll split them up. I'll go upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all going after him because of the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, keep going!\NYou can do this in ten minutes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Got the answers you asked me for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Five transformed devils, all at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai, please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki's on the third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There were two devils after him.\NIf you don't hurry, they'll get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,His wound is closed over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that because he bit me?\NBecause he drank blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have killed them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's little Nine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Copying the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I made him lock the door; he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I did that background check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you were on A Squad,\Nyou spent 5 years in W Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My connections in Division 5 got me some info\Nfrom people who were in W Squad at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and they confirmed that there was\Na Megumi Ishimaru on the squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But only for one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency message for Public Security\NDivision 5 Squads L through N.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We received a report that several armed officers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,are devil hunting in an abandoned building\Nat 2-6 Hinomi, Koto Ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's in 2A2B jurisdiction.\NThey'll be on the scene shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagi, get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? He said "devil hunting"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure, but apparently this was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean we can leave you stranded there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought in eight homeless men,\Nseven devils and one human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Three of them were killed by Division 5 bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,On the scene, unauthorized, were armed members\Nof F Squad, who had lured the men inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All ready for framing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to tell them what we're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll know we're not really hunting devils!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll also know that we let Nine and Seven\Nin on our plans without authorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They might remove us from the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you tricked us into raiding the hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The date and time of the raid were your idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jason did not report on today's operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I crying about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say "Jason"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Number 13: Jason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you; you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to be happy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you been plotting all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That first man, the one who shot the devil and ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect he was working for Kikuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be that they've been\Nwatching me the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think they were capable of setting\Nsuch an annoying trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The way things are going, normally,\NI'd expect the list to have been deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nine is copying the list right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he is. There was a list.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I joined the CCC and\NDivision 5, to find that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an undercover agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I really work for...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Public Security General Affairs,\NInvestigation Division 6, Section 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,there's one more undercover agent working for us,\Nprobably the one who left us the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He infiltrated the CCC just like I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Makimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm turning you in to HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Turning me in? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll arrest you, too, for the murders\Nyou committed at Cross Bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm turning myself in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,E Squad investigated at Cross Bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They found bullets and a revolver\Nwith the manager's fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was gunshot residue\Non the manager's right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Makimura would have been trying to\Nget everyone in the bar to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That probably made the manager\Neven more suspicious, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She carried a gun for self-defense,\Nand she fired first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But then what about the employee?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens a lot with vampires who have seen\Ndeath or injury caused by blood drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When they see someone they care about\Nlosing a lot of blood right in front of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,they're so afraid of losing control\Nthat they kill themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Makimura was a double agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And so was Ishimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me. I'm taking you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Anzai. There are squad cars down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not just the riot police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the media's here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just speculation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but I feel like there's some other motive\Nbehind this trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:18:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If all he needed was the list, Makimura could have\Njust taken the whole computer and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe that's not all he needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The list has accounting information.\NIn other words, the flow of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It only lists members that have\Na financial connection to the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there someone involved\Nthat we won't find with just a list?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something behind the CCC.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I thought Zero One was pulling the strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A self-righteous politician or\Ngovernment official at worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But something doesn't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something bigger... like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe R2PC?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And the government body over them,\Nthe Ministry of Health, Labor, and Welfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe what Makimura really wanted\Nwas to get everyone's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why he called the police and the press?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can cause all the uproar you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Get people from all walks of life to notice the CCC.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't solve the fundamental problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't stop F Squad or Section 11...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because I was betting on\Na one in a million chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The chance that they might\Nget to the truth of this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems I overestimated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the MHLW?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Or there's something else...\Nsomething more than-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you think you can solve this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,by cutting off the lizard's head\Ninstead of its tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But this lizard can regrow even its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like grass; you mow it down,\Nbut you leave the roots, so it grows back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The roots are down in the ground\Nwhere you can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't pull them out,\Nand you can't control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, they all come together\Nin a large mass to form a giant grassy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The enormous, uncontrollable...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"shared consciousness"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,forming society's roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I've seen that building. I think it's in my neighborhood. Scary!\N{\an5}Looks like the devils are freaking out and killing people again.\N{\an5}Anyway, here's a picture of the scene!\Nit's the stereotype that "devils are dangerous."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}All devils should die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as people accept this stereotype,\Nit doesn't matter if you crush the CCC.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else will be forced to step in\Nand take their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I choose to stay inside this box,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and use the CCC to fight against those at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't build anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,by committing murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This little chat has gone on long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time we end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's draw the curtain on this act.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Still there, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That little...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai's been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,On the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A sniper hit Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai? Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai! Hey! Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I... dying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai! Anzai, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in, Anzai! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't do something, he's a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If they transform and engage in violence,\Ncause injury, or drink blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know if they'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of their reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they will be forbidden to make contact\Nwith humans for the foreseeable future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Taira!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee, get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to him. Take me to Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:22:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like softly melting away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.76,0:22:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could have loved each other more like that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What could I have told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A chance encounter that cannot amount to love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone forgive me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this filthy form is who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.59,0:22:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these fingers trembling as they touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story of fighting together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hold you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect you without hurting you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You and only you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.59,0:22:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story of desiring forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.17,0:23:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will keep fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Against the urges surging up inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.34,0:23:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, again, I..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep red dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we're softly melting away...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,DEVILS' LINE,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.13,0:23:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Line 12,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"DEVILS' LINE."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.96,0:23:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}DEVILS' LINE